WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.430
Hey, good morning family. I have another

00:00:02.440 --> 00:00:05.269
video for you all today. I want

00:00:05.279 --> 00:00:07.389
to talk to you about being the

00:00:07.399 --> 00:00:10.629
friend of God and more so what that

00:00:10.639 --> 00:00:13.430
means to me, but what I feel

00:00:13.440 --> 00:00:15.390
in my heart that you all need to know.

00:00:15.400 --> 00:00:17.109
I pray for people, like I told

00:00:17.119 --> 00:00:19.950
you last video, whenever I

00:00:19.960 --> 00:00:21.509
talk to people on the phone, the Lord

00:00:21.519 --> 00:00:24.870
will reveal things to me about them.

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:27.669
It was interesting because I was

00:00:27.679 --> 00:00:30.669
asking the Lord about an individual

00:00:30.679 --> 00:00:35.110
and He said, "Brandon, I don't know them.

00:00:35.120 --> 00:00:37.389
I used to know them, but I don't know

00:00:37.399 --> 00:00:40.750
them anymore."That took me back and I

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:42.389
said, "Well, Lord, what do you mean by

00:00:42.389 --> 00:00:42.399
that?"He

00:00:42.399 --> 00:00:45.430
said, "Brandon, how do you know

00:00:45.440 --> 00:00:48.510
somebody? How do you get to know

00:00:48.510 --> 00:00:48.520
somebody?"I

00:00:48.520 --> 00:00:51.110
said, "Well, Lord, you spend

00:00:51.120 --> 00:00:53.750
time with them. You're intimate with

00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:54.910
them."He

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:57.670
said, "Do the people that watch your

00:00:57.670 --> 00:00:57.680
videos—you've

00:00:57.680 --> 00:00:59.670
made over 100

00:00:59.670 --> 00:00:59.680
videos—do

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:02.430
you feel like they know you?"I said,

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:04.990
"No, Lord, they don't know me at all.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:06.670
They may know a lot

00:01:06.680 --> 00:01:08.830
about me, my

00:01:08.840 --> 00:01:12.270
history,

00:01:12.280 --> 00:01:15.070
and things that You've done

00:01:15.080 --> 00:01:18.030
for me, but do they truly know

00:01:18.030 --> 00:01:18.040
you?"I

00:01:18.040 --> 00:01:20.670
said, "No, not at all."They don't know the

00:01:20.680 --> 00:01:24.310
intimacy that my wife and I have.

00:01:24.320 --> 00:01:27.830
How is that developed? It is developed

00:01:27.840 --> 00:01:31.590
day by day in intimacy and a friendship,

00:01:31.600 --> 00:01:34.710
just like a marriage is developed day by

00:01:34.720 --> 00:01:36.469
day. If you hear any noises, it's my

00:01:36.479 --> 00:01:38.469
daughter again, Megan; she's sitting

00:01:38.479 --> 00:01:41.109
in here watching

00:01:41.109 --> 00:01:41.119
VeggieTales.

00:01:41.119 --> 00:01:46.310
Intimacy is developed day by day; it

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:51.149
is never an overnight thing. Like

00:01:51.159 --> 00:01:53.230
I said, you met your

00:01:53.240 --> 00:01:55.030
husband or your wife and you had a

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:57.350
courtship. You were so excited to go on

00:01:57.360 --> 00:01:59.870
these dates and the relationship was

00:01:59.880 --> 00:02:02.709
fresh; you had those puppy dog eyes and you

00:02:02.709 --> 00:02:02.719
were

00:02:02.719 --> 00:02:04.990
excited to go out to the

00:02:04.990 --> 00:02:05.000
movies or

00:02:05.000 --> 00:02:06.830
go out to

00:02:10.000 --> 00:02:12.790
dinner.

00:02:12.800 --> 00:02:14.470
You have that relationship, that

00:02:14.480 --> 00:02:16.630
courtship, and you're excited about

00:02:16.630 --> 00:02:16.640
that

00:02:16.640 --> 00:02:17.949
relationship, but when you get

00:02:17.959 --> 00:02:19.869
married, there's an intimacy that

00:02:19.879 --> 00:02:21.790
develops beyond a boyfriend and

00:02:21.800 --> 00:02:23.790
girlfriend, beyond anything you can

00:02:23.800 --> 00:02:25.589
comprehend. Of course, if

00:02:25.599 --> 00:02:27.390
you've been married for a while, you

00:02:27.390 --> 00:02:27.400
know—I've

00:02:27.400 --> 00:02:30.150
been married 23

00:02:30.150 --> 00:02:30.160
years—so

00:02:30.160 --> 00:02:33.470
you start to really know that

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:37.030
individual:

00:02:37.040 --> 00:02:39.630
their likes,

00:02:39.640 --> 00:02:42.869
their facial expressions,

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:45.550
the smells, everything. You know

00:02:45.560 --> 00:02:49.589
that individual, but it is developed over

00:02:49.599 --> 00:02:53.790
time; it is not developed in a day.

00:02:53.800 --> 00:02:55.149
So a lot of

00:02:55.159 --> 00:02:58.430
people think they go to church on a

00:02:58.440 --> 00:03:00.149
Sunday, and that's what the Lord

00:03:00.159 --> 00:03:02.470
shows me. They go to church on a Sunday,

00:03:02.480 --> 00:03:05.149
they may volunteer maybe once a month,

00:03:05.159 --> 00:03:08.990
and they have an hour service. They go

00:03:09.000 --> 00:03:11.710
to that hour service, they may pray for

00:03:11.710 --> 00:03:11.720
ten

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:14.589
minutes a

00:03:14.599 --> 00:03:17.630
day, and they may read their

00:03:17.640 --> 00:03:20.589
Bible for five minutes a day. But just

00:03:20.599 --> 00:03:23.990
think about this: imagine if you did

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:27.030
that exact same thing with your spouse

00:03:27.040 --> 00:03:30.229
or your loved one

00:03:30.239 --> 00:03:32.789
and you only talked to them five minutes a

00:03:32.799 --> 00:03:35.830
day. Your main conversation was about an

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.190
hour on

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:40.509
Sundays when you go to church; after that,

00:03:40.519 --> 00:03:42.630
you

00:03:42.640 --> 00:03:45.190
have some fellowship

00:03:45.200 --> 00:03:47.630
at dinner, and then you don't

00:03:47.640 --> 00:03:49.350
talk to them anymore but maybe five

00:03:49.360 --> 00:03:51.830
or ten minutes a day from

00:03:51.840 --> 00:03:54.509
then on—never on the phone,

00:03:54.509 --> 00:03:54.519
nothing—and

00:03:54.519 --> 00:03:56.789
you're

00:03:56.799 --> 00:03:59.149
doing all the talking. You're rehearsing

00:03:59.159 --> 00:04:01.949
everything that you want from them:

00:04:01.959 --> 00:04:04.309
"I need this and this and this. God,

00:04:04.319 --> 00:04:05.830
I thank you that you healed Johnny and

00:04:05.840 --> 00:04:07.429
you're healing Susie, and you're

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:09.710
going after this one who is lost.

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:11.429
Lord, I have all these needs,

00:04:11.429 --> 00:04:11.439
and

00:04:11.439 --> 00:04:13.110
I'm not feeling well

00:04:13.120 --> 00:04:15.789
in my body today. Lord, I

00:04:15.799 --> 00:04:19.189
have all this stuff going on at work;

00:04:19.199 --> 00:04:21.509
my boss is a

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:23.469
real jerk and I've got

00:04:25.680 --> 00:04:27.710
this deadline. Could you help me with

00:04:27.720 --> 00:04:30.189
some money?"Then you turn

00:04:30.199 --> 00:04:32.189
around and say, "Amen,"and then you're gone.

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:33.510
He doesn't hear from you

00:04:33.520 --> 00:04:36.150
anymore that day other than when you

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:38.590
need something again. Every single

00:04:38.600 --> 00:04:40.629
time you go to the Lord, you need

00:04:40.639 --> 00:04:41.590
something

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:44.189
again. You don't really ever hear His

00:04:44.199 --> 00:04:47.990
heart. Prayer is a two-way conversation; He's

00:04:48.000 --> 00:04:49.550
going to talk to you and you're going to

00:04:49.560 --> 00:04:51.510
talk to Him.

00:04:51.520 --> 00:04:54.909
But most people think prayer is

00:04:54.919 --> 00:04:57.510
just baby steps.

00:04:57.520 --> 00:05:00.029
This is like little children stuff:

00:05:00.039 --> 00:05:01.990
"Father, I need, I need, I need;

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:03.790
I have wants and desires.

00:05:03.800 --> 00:05:05.469
Bye!"But

00:05:05.479 --> 00:05:08.270
if you want to grow up in the

00:05:08.280 --> 00:05:10.310
relationship and you want to come up to

00:05:10.320 --> 00:05:12.710
a higher place with Him... people say,

00:05:12.720 --> 00:05:14.909
"How do you see in the spirit? How do you

00:05:14.919 --> 00:05:17.510
have visitations from

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:19.230
angels? How have you had eight

00:05:19.240 --> 00:05:21.710
visitations from Jesus? How have you seen

00:05:21.720 --> 00:05:24.150
into the throne room like

00:05:24.160 --> 00:05:27.590
that? I want you to help me

00:05:27.600 --> 00:05:30.029
to get there

00:05:30.029 --> 00:05:30.039
because

00:05:30.039 --> 00:05:31.749
I don't know how to get

00:05:31.759 --> 00:05:35.350
there. I don't hear God."I

00:05:35.350 --> 00:05:35.360
read

00:05:35.360 --> 00:05:37.510
so many comments in the comment

00:05:37.520 --> 00:05:40.309
section from

00:05:40.309 --> 00:05:40.319
people

00:05:40.319 --> 00:05:43.510
asking me how

00:05:43.510 --> 00:05:43.520
to

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:44.870
hear

00:05:44.880 --> 00:05:48.150
God. It is developed. It says,

00:05:48.160 --> 00:05:51.790
"Those that seek me will find me; those

00:05:51.800 --> 00:05:54.950
that knock, I'll open the door unto

00:05:54.960 --> 00:05:56.749
him."Relationship

00:05:56.759 --> 00:06:02.070
is developed day to day,

00:06:02.080 --> 00:06:05.070
all day long. The Bible says to

00:06:05.080 --> 00:06:07.110
pray without

00:06:07.120 --> 00:06:11.029
ceasing. Seeking Him and finding Him

00:06:13.039 --> 00:06:16.350
automatically tells me that God is

00:06:16.360 --> 00:06:19.189
hiding in some way. It's like hide and

00:06:19.199 --> 00:06:22.990
seek. "God, where are you? I want to be

00:06:23.000 --> 00:06:25.070
intimate with you. I want to go to

00:06:25.080 --> 00:06:28.029
another level. What's on your heart?"People ask

00:06:28.029 --> 00:06:28.039
if I

00:06:28.039 --> 00:06:29.909
pray a certain way to

00:06:29.919 --> 00:06:32.629
get Him to show me things.

00:06:32.639 --> 00:06:34.909
I want to say it like this:

00:06:34.919 --> 00:06:41.469
not one time do I ever pray

00:06:41.479 --> 00:06:44.230
with the intentions of seeking and

00:06:44.240 --> 00:06:49.110
seeing. If I pray, I'm praying because I'm

00:06:49.120 --> 00:06:50.950
intimate. I

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:55.350
want to touch His garment. I want

00:06:55.360 --> 00:06:59.189
what's on His heart. "Lord, what's on your

00:06:59.199 --> 00:07:04.230
heart today? Let me help

00:07:04.240 --> 00:07:08.510
you. What is grieving you

00:07:08.520 --> 00:07:10.990
today? What's your

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:14.270
agenda, not my agenda?"I don't pray for

00:07:14.280 --> 00:07:17.350
Him to touch my agenda; I pray for His

00:07:17.360 --> 00:07:19.270
agenda for

00:07:19.280 --> 00:07:22.869
me, mirroring it back and saying, "God, not

00:07:22.879 --> 00:07:26.990
my will but Yours be done."How can I come

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:30.790
up higher in my thinking?

00:07:30.800 --> 00:07:34.510
The Bible says that you have the mind of

00:07:34.520 --> 00:07:38.710
Christ. You can think like Christ thinks

00:07:38.720 --> 00:07:42.510
by meditating on His word,

00:07:42.520 --> 00:07:45.149
getting scripture inside of you.

00:07:45.159 --> 00:07:49.390
I try very

00:07:49.400 --> 00:07:52.110
seldom to—and I'm just being real

00:07:52.110 --> 00:07:52.120
with y'all—I

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:54.149
get in the flesh too

00:07:54.159 --> 00:07:55.309
and I go to him and say, "Lord, I have

00:07:55.319 --> 00:07:57.629
needs. I need my puppies to sell. I need

00:07:57.639 --> 00:08:00.469
all this

00:08:00.469 --> 00:08:00.479
stuff."But

00:08:00.479 --> 00:08:03.550
He said He

00:08:03.560 --> 00:08:05.990
knows you have need of things before

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:07.309
you even

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:10.950
ask. Jesus

00:08:10.960 --> 00:08:13.710
said, "Our Father, who

00:08:13.720 --> 00:08:15.469
art in heaven, hallowed be thy name. Thy

00:08:15.479 --> 00:08:17.230
kingdom come, thy will be

00:08:17.230 --> 00:08:17.240
done."He

00:08:17.240 --> 00:08:20.510
knows everything

00:08:20.520 --> 00:08:24.710
you need before you even ask it. So

00:08:24.720 --> 00:08:27.029
I go to Him not insulting Him,

00:08:27.029 --> 00:08:27.039
but thanking

00:08:27.039 --> 00:08:30.189
Him for it.

00:08:30.199 --> 00:08:32.469
"Thank you, Father, for healing

00:08:32.479 --> 00:08:35.269
for my family. No colds, no viruses, no

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:37.469
nothing come nigh. I thank you, Father, that

00:08:37.479 --> 00:08:39.870
your word says that by your stripes we

00:08:39.880 --> 00:08:42.909
are healed.

00:08:45.760 --> 00:08:48.710
I thank you,

00:08:48.720 --> 00:08:51.110
Father, that you said in your word that

00:08:51.120 --> 00:08:54.350
those that seek you will find you. Now,

00:08:54.360 --> 00:08:57.030
Father, whatever is on your heart today, I

00:08:57.040 --> 00:08:59.150
thank you that I pray the

00:08:59.160 --> 00:09:02.110
mysteries and the secret things. And if

00:09:02.120 --> 00:09:05.470
you have anything to show me today, Lord,

00:09:05.480 --> 00:09:08.310
not in the flesh, I thank you that I see

00:09:08.320 --> 00:09:10.389
what I'm supposed to see and I hear what I'm

00:09:10.399 --> 00:09:13.750
supposed to hear from You, that You said

00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:16.269
I will hear Your voice and a stranger's

00:09:16.279 --> 00:09:20.150
voice I'll not follow. Now, Satan, I bind

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:23.350
you in the name of Jesus and I command

00:09:23.360 --> 00:09:26.509
you to bow your knee. You get out of here,

00:09:26.519 --> 00:09:28.990
you leave me alone. I plead the blood

00:09:29.000 --> 00:09:31.630
over my prayer time and I plead the blood

00:09:31.640 --> 00:09:33.910
over me that I hear the Lord's voice and

00:09:33.920 --> 00:09:35.750
I'm not going to be tormented by the

00:09:35.750 --> 00:09:35.760
tormentor."I

00:09:35.760 --> 00:09:38.389
go to Him with

00:09:38.399 --> 00:09:41.310
worship.

00:09:41.320 --> 00:09:44.230
What really blesses me is Kim

00:09:44.240 --> 00:09:46.550
Clement. He has worship things on

00:09:46.560 --> 00:09:49.790
YouTube and I listen to him

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:52.350
worshiping on "The Mountain of the

00:09:52.350 --> 00:09:52.360
Lord."I

00:09:52.360 --> 00:09:55.389
record it on my phone and I

00:09:55.399 --> 00:09:57.550
put it on

00:09:57.560 --> 00:10:00.990
repeat,

00:10:01.000 --> 00:10:03.069
just hearing him talk about the

00:10:03.079 --> 00:10:05.069
mountain of the Lord.

00:10:12.560 --> 00:10:14.910
I feel the presence of the Lord so

00:10:14.920 --> 00:10:17.269
strong whenever that man sings, and

00:10:17.279 --> 00:10:18.790
he

00:10:18.800 --> 00:10:21.350
went home to be with the Lord years ago. I

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:24.829
listen to that and I listen to

00:10:24.839 --> 00:10:27.269
piano music, like "I

00:10:27.279 --> 00:10:30.150
Surrender

00:10:30.150 --> 00:10:30.160
All."You

00:10:30.160 --> 00:10:31.670
just get in the presence of the

00:10:31.680 --> 00:10:33.590
Lord.

00:10:41.160 --> 00:10:44.110
Find what ministers to you and gets

00:10:44.110 --> 00:10:44.120
you

00:10:44.120 --> 00:10:47.110
in that river.

00:10:52.839 --> 00:10:54.990
Think

00:10:55.000 --> 00:10:59.629
about Lot in Sodom and Gomorrah.

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:01.990
Lot was Abraham's

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:06.870
nephew.

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:12.750
He's in the midst of all the trash

00:11:12.760 --> 00:11:16.629
going on and doesn't even know that

00:11:16.639 --> 00:11:19.069
Sodom and Gomorrah is about to be judged

00:11:19.079 --> 00:11:21.710
and wiped off the face of the Earth.

00:11:24.920 --> 00:11:27.750
But God comes to Abraham because

00:11:27.760 --> 00:11:30.069
he's His friend.

00:11:30.079 --> 00:11:32.310
God will come to you and start speaking

00:11:32.320 --> 00:11:34.990
to you and showing you the hidden

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:37.350
things. There's a lot of things

00:11:37.360 --> 00:11:39.230
I probably shouldn't say on here,

00:11:39.240 --> 00:11:42.710
but out of compassion, I try to

00:11:42.720 --> 00:11:45.470
tell you all what's coming

00:11:45.470 --> 00:11:45.480
and

00:11:45.480 --> 00:11:47.990
what to pray about.

00:11:55.360 --> 00:11:57.190
Some of this stuff people

00:11:57.200 --> 00:11:59.310
are not ready for. There are some of

00:11:59.320 --> 00:12:00.670
you that are mature and

00:12:00.680 --> 00:12:01.790
understand, but there

00:12:01.790 --> 00:12:01.800
are

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:03.750
a lot of babies on here that

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:06.310
don't know, so I'm trying to take you to

00:12:06.320 --> 00:12:07.629
the next

00:12:07.639 --> 00:12:10.829
level, teaching you about being a friend

00:12:10.839 --> 00:12:13.910
of God. When the

00:12:13.920 --> 00:12:16.629
Bible says that Jesus says, "Depart from

00:12:16.639 --> 00:12:19.509
me, I never knew you,"people say, "Lord, I

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:21.629
healed the sick in your name and cast out

00:12:21.639 --> 00:12:24.509
devils in your

00:12:24.509 --> 00:12:24.519
name."But

00:12:24.519 --> 00:12:27.030
He says to you

00:12:27.040 --> 00:12:29.269
at the end, "Depart from me,

00:12:29.279 --> 00:12:30.509
I never knew

00:12:30.509 --> 00:12:30.519
you."He

00:12:30.519 --> 00:12:34.910
never knew you. That means you can

00:12:40.120 --> 00:12:43.189
have a relationship with somebody

00:12:43.199 --> 00:12:46.550
and talk to them, but they don't know

00:12:46.560 --> 00:12:50.870
you. You can have a conversation at

00:12:50.880 --> 00:12:53.470
church, but you still don't know Him. You

00:12:53.480 --> 00:12:55.870
probably do not know your pastor;

00:12:55.880 --> 00:12:57.550
he

00:12:57.560 --> 00:12:58.829
preaches at you for

00:12:58.839 --> 00:13:00.110
an hour every

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:02.670
Sunday, but

00:13:02.680 --> 00:13:05.030
you don't know his intimacy

00:13:05.040 --> 00:13:07.110
behind closed

00:13:07.110 --> 00:13:07.120
doors.

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:09.269
You can get to know

00:13:09.279 --> 00:13:12.670
the Father in a relationship that deep,

00:13:12.670 --> 00:13:12.680
where

00:13:12.680 --> 00:13:14.870
He will come and start

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:17.069
sharing the

00:13:17.079 --> 00:13:22.189
hidden things and the secret

00:13:22.199 --> 00:13:24.590
things

00:13:24.590 --> 00:13:24.600
that

